<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Henrique Design – Especialista en diseño de interiores y mobiliario a medida en Sueca, Valencia.">
  <title>Henrique Design | Interiorismo y Mobiliario</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (display) + DM Sans (body) -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* ==========================================================================
       VARIABLES GLOBALES Y RESET
       ========================================================================== */
    :root {
      --color-primario:    #18181b;   /* Negro cálido */
      --color-secundario:  #b45309;   /* Ámbar oscuro */
      --color-acento:      #d97706;   /* Ámbar vivo */
      --color-fondo:       #fafaf9;   /* Crema muy suave */
      --color-fondo-alt:   #f5f5f4;   /* Piedra clara */
      --color-texto:       #3f3f46;
      --color-texto-suave: #71717a;
      --color-blanco:      #ffffff;
      --color-borde:       #e4e4e7;

      --fuente-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      --fuente-body:    'DM Sans', sans-serif;

      --radio:       8px;
      --radio-lg:    16px;
      --sombra:      0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --sombra-lg:   0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      --transicion:  all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--fuente-body);
      background-color: var(--color-fondo);
      color: var(--color-texto);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       SISTEMA DE NAVEGACIÓN SOLO CSS (Radio Button Hack)
       ========================================================================== */
    input[type="radio"][name="navegacion"] {
      display: none;
    }

    .pagina {
      display: none;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
      animation: fadeUp 0.45s ease forwards;
    }

    /* Página visible según el radio activo */
    #nav-inicio:checked      ~ #pagina-inicio,
    #nav-portfolio:checked   ~ #pagina-portfolio,
    #nav-presupuesto:checked ~ #pagina-presupuesto,
    #nav-contacto:checked    ~ #pagina-contacto {
      display: block;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       CABECERA
       ========================================================================== */
    header {
      background-color: var(--color-primario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      height: 80px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    /* Logotipo */
    .logo {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .logo span {
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--color-acento);
    }

    /* Menú */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    nav label {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: var(--transicion);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }

    nav label:hover {
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    /* Estado activo en menú */
    #nav-inicio:checked      ~ header nav label[for="nav-inicio"],
    #nav-portfolio:checked   ~ header nav label[for="nav-portfolio"],
    #nav-presupuesto:checked ~ header nav label[for="nav-presupuesto"],
    #nav-contacto:checked    ~ header nav label[for="nav-contacto"] {
      color: var(--color-acento);
      background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.12);
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       COMPONENTES COMPARTIDOS
       ========================================================================== */
    .seccion-titulo {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-primario);
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .seccion-subtitulo {
      color: var(--color-texto-suave);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .etiqueta {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-secundario);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .btn-primario {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--color-secundario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radio);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: var(--transicion);
    }

    .btn-primario:hover {
      background: var(--color-acento);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.3);
    }

    .divisor {
      width: 48px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--color-secundario);
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       PÁGINA 1: INICIO
       ========================================================================== */

    /* — Hero — */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(24,24,27,0.65) 0%, rgba(24,24,27,0.5) 100%),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618221195710-dd6b41faaea6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      min-height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 4rem clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-acento);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.1;
      max-width: 12ch;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      max-width: 480px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* — Sobre Mí — */
    .sobre-mi {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6rem clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
      background: var(--color-blanco);
    }

    .sobre-mi-texto p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-texto);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .sobre-mi-imagen img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 480px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: var(--radio-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra-lg);
    }

    /* — Servicios — */
    .servicios {
      padding: 6rem clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
      background: var(--color-fondo-alt);
    }

    .servicios-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .servicios-header .divisor {
      margin: 1rem auto;
    }

    .grid-servicios {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .servicio-card {
      background: var(--color-blanco);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radio-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-borde);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      transition: var(--transicion);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .servicio-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--color-secundario);
      transform: scaleY(0);
      transform-origin: bottom;
      transition: var(--transicion);
    }

    .servicio-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra-lg);
    }

    .servicio-card:hover::before {
      transform: scaleY(1);
    }

    .servicio-icono {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .servicio-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--color-primario);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .servicio-card p {
      color: var(--color-texto-suave);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       PÁGINA 2: PORTFOLIO
       ========================================================================== */
    .portfolio-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
    }

    .portfolio-header .divisor { margin: 1rem auto; }

    /* Filtros de categoría (solo visual, CSS puro) */
    .portfolio-categorias {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 0 2rem 2rem;
    }

    .cat-badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      padding: 0.45rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--color-blanco);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-borde);
      color: var(--color-texto-suave);
      cursor: default;
    }

    .cat-badge.activo {
      background: var(--color-primario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      border-color: var(--color-primario);
    }

    /* Grid de galería */
    .galeria-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 6rem) 5rem;
    }

    .item-galeria {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: var(--radio-lg);
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      box-shadow: var(--sombra);
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .item-galeria img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    .item-galeria:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    .capa-galeria {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(24,24,27,0.85) 0%, transparent 60%);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: var(--transicion);
    }

    .item-galeria:hover .capa-galeria {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .capa-galeria .cat-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-acento);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .capa-galeria h3 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       PÁGINA 3: PRESUPUESTO
       ========================================================================== */
    .presupuesto-wrapper {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(24,24,27,0.55), rgba(24,24,27,0.55)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618221195710-dd6b41faaea6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=40');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .contenedor-form {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 580px;
      background: var(--color-blanco);
      padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
      border-radius: var(--radio-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--sombra-lg);
    }

    .contenedor-form .etiqueta { display: block; }

    .contenedor-form h2 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--color-primario);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contenedor-form > p {
      color: var(--color-texto-suave);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .grupo-form {
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .grupo-form label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-primario);
    }

    .grupo-form input[type="text"],
    .grupo-form input[type="email"],
    .grupo-form input[type="tel"],
    .grupo-form select,
    .grupo-form textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--color-borde);
      border-radius: var(--radio);
      font-family: var(--fuente-body);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--color-texto);
      background: var(--color-fondo);
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
      outline: none;
    }

    .grupo-form input:focus,
    .grupo-form select:focus,
    .grupo-form textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--color-secundario);
      background: var(--color-blanco);
    }

    .grupo-form textarea {
      resize: vertical;
      min-height: 110px;
    }

    .grupo-checkbox {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--color-texto-suave);
    }

    .grupo-checkbox input { margin-top: 3px; }

    .grupo-checkbox a {
      color: var(--color-secundario);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       PÁGINA 4: CONTACTO
       ========================================================================== */
    .contacto-wrapper {
      padding: 4rem clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 6rem) 6rem;
    }

    .contacto-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .contacto-header .divisor { margin: 1rem auto; }

    .contenedor-contacto {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      border-radius: var(--radio-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--sombra-lg);
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .datos-empresa {
      background: var(--color-primario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    }

    .datos-empresa h2 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: var(--color-acento);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .item-dato {
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .item-dato strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-acento);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .item-dato span {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    }

    .redes-contacto {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .redes-contacto a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      transition: var(--transicion);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .redes-contacto a:hover {
      background: var(--color-secundario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
    }

    .mapa-empresa {
      min-height: 420px;
    }

    .mapa-empresa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       FOOTER
       ========================================================================== */
    footer {
      background: var(--color-primario);
      color: #71717a;
      padding: 3.5rem clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 8rem) 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #27272a;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-col h4 {
      font-family: var(--fuente-display);
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-blanco);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .footer-col p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .redes-sociales {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .redes-sociales a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      background: #27272a;
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: var(--transicion);
    }

    .redes-sociales a:hover {
      background: var(--color-secundario);
      color: var(--color-blanco);
    }

    .aviso-legal a {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #71717a;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .aviso-legal a:hover {
      color: var(--color-acento);
    }

    .footer-copy {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #52525b;
    }

    /* ==========================================================================
       RESPONSIVE
       ========================================================================== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .sobre-mi {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }

      .sobre-mi-imagen img {
        height: 280px;
      }

      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        height: auto;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }

      nav label {
        padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }

      .hero {
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        min-height: 65vh;
      }

      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }

      .contenedor-form {
        padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem;
      }

      .contenedor-contacto {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .mapa-empresa {
        min-height: 300px;
      }

      .galeria-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        padding: 0 1rem 3rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .galeria-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- =====================================================================
       CONTROLES DE NAVEGACIÓN (Solo CSS – Radio Button Hack)
       ===================================================================== -->
  <input type="radio" name="navegacion" id="nav-inicio"      checked>
  <input type="radio" name="navegacion" id="nav-portfolio">
  <input type="radio" name="navegacion" id="nav-presupuesto">
  <input type="radio" name="navegacion" id="nav-contacto">

  <!-- =====================================================================
       CABECERA / NAVEGACIÓN PRINCIPAL
       ===================================================================== -->
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HENRIQUE <span>DESIGN</span></div>
    <nav aria-label="Menú principal">
      <label for="nav-inicio">Inicio</label>
      <label for="nav-portfolio">Portfolio</label>
      <label for="nav-presupuesto">Presupuesto</label>
      <label for="nav-contacto">Contacto</label>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- =====================================================================
       PÁGINA 1: INICIO
       ===================================================================== -->
  <main id="pagina-inicio" class="pagina">

    <!-- Sección 1: Hero -->
    <section class="hero" aria-label="Portada">
      <p class="hero-kicker">Diseño de Interiores · Sueca, Valencia</p>
      <h1>Diseño que Transforma Espacios</h1>
      <p>Especialista en interiores funcionales y mobiliario a medida, llevando la elegancia de los planos a la realidad.</p>
      <label for="nav-portfolio" class="btn-primario" role="button" aria-label="Ver portfolio">
        Ver Portfolio →
      </label>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección 2: Sobre Mí -->
    <section class="sobre-mi" aria-labelledby="titulo-sobre-mi">
      <article class="sobre-mi-texto">
        <span class="etiqueta">Sobre mí</span>
        <h2 id="titulo-sobre-mi" class="seccion-titulo">Henrique da Costa Gomes</h2>
        <div class="divisor"></div>
        <p>Soy profesional del diseño con amplia experiencia en el desarrollo integral de proyectos de interiores y mobiliario, desde la conceptualización hasta la entrega final.</p>
        <p>Me apasiona la creación de espacios funcionales y estéticamente atractivos, aplicando mis conocimientos en interpretación de planos y dirección de montajes a medida.</p>
        <br>
        <label for="nav-contacto" class="btn-primario" role="button">Contactar →</label>
      </article>
      <figure class="sobre-mi-imagen">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1631679706909-1844bbd07221?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
          alt="Sala de estar moderna diseñada por Henrique"
          loading="lazy">
      </figure>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección 3: Servicios -->
    <section class="servicios" aria-labelledby="titulo-servicios">
      <header class="servicios-header">
        <span class="etiqueta">Lo que ofrezco</span>
        <h2 id="titulo-servicios" class="seccion-titulo">Mis Servicios</h2>
        <div class="divisor"></div>
      </header>
      <div class="grid-servicios">
        <article class="servicio-card">
          <div class="servicio-icono" aria-hidden="true">🏡</div>
          <h3>Diseño de Interiores</h3>
          <p>Conceptualización, selección de materiales y distribución de espacios residenciales y comerciales adaptados a cada cliente.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="servicio-card">
